notesStmt.note: This is a meeting of representatives of various European organizations and networks involved in higher education quality assurance. After the general opening and an introductory round, S7, S6 and S4 present their respective networks, then a discussion follows. S1, S4, S5 and S11 are well acquainted, the others are not, even though they might have run into each other on other occasions. Generally, there is a friendly atmosphere though participants are competitors in some way. S1 is the chairman and clearly assigns turns. S2 is the researcher and does not participate in the meeting.

equipment.p: 3 portable minidisk recorders with electret condenser stereo microphone and a cassette recorder
